-- Merkel praises Danish PM, says euro outsiders can head EU Council
-- By Michelle Martin
-- Thu Jun 19, 2014 07:57AM EDT
-- None



BERLIN, June 19 (Reuters) - German Chancellor Angela Merkel heaped praise on Danish Prime Minister Helle Thorning-Schmidt on Thursday and said there was no reason a president of the European Council should not come from an EU country outside of the euro zone - such as Denmark.

